examples: I nudged her but she didn't react.
Le di un codazo pero ella no reaccionó.
You never know how he is going to react.
Nunca se sabe cómo va a reaccionar.
He would have reacted in the same way.
Él habría reaccionado de la misma forma.
Local residents have reacted angrily to the news.
Los residentes locales han reaccionado con enojo a la noticia.
